---
import ActPlateHeader from './ActPlateHeader.astro';
---
<section id="about" class="sec" data-reveal>
  <ActPlateHeader label="About" />
  <p>
    <strong>OpenGGF</strong> is an open-source, OpenGL-accelerated game engine written in Java that
    faithfully reimplements the classic 16-bit <em>Sonic the Hedgehog</em> games — physics, collision,
    rendering, and audio are all verified against community-maintained disassemblies for accuracy.
  </p>
  <p>
    It runs from your own legally-obtained ROM images. <span class="muted">Not affiliated with Sega;
    no copyrighted assets are included.</span>
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .sec { padding: clamp(40px, 7vh, 64px) 24px; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .sec p { font: 400 clamp(15px, 1.8vw, 19px)/1.7 var(--font-body); color: #2b2b33; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .sec p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .sec strong { font-weight: 800; }
  .sec em { font-style: italic; }
  .muted { color: #777; }
</style>
